      <title>Men of Mecca Event - Men of the Mecca Leadership Council Convening </title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52515393079482/huge/ce070e8ad7518077cf259dbe194db0c2027cedbf.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Mon, 06 Apr 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>We have established the Men of the Mecca Leadership Council, a representative body comprised of leaders from male student organizations across campus, including cultural groups, LGBTQ  organizations, and athletic teams. The Council will hold its inaugural convening on April 6. The purpose of this group is threefold: to build community among men across the University, to serve as a direct advisory body to the administration on the needs and priorities of the male student population, and to collaborate with University leadership on strategies related to recruitment, retention, and successful matriculation.</p>

