ain campus community to the law school for this important dialogue.%0A%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fevents.howard.edu%2Fevent%2Frace-ai-and-modern-day-redlining-a-conversation-with-jon-seward-and-kristen-clarke%0A">Email this event</a></p></div></div>]]></description>
