      <title>Research Month Opening Celebration  at The Interdisciplinary Research Building </title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52509430316436/huge/dc30621ff572f8cb514dec9191a61f2eaf6044b1.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Mon, 06 Apr 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>Join the Office of Research for the Research Month Opening Social. The University community is invited to celebrate the start of Research Month at our Opening Social — an engaging gathering designed to bring faculty, students, staff, and partners together in a relaxed and welcoming environment. Enjoy food and refreshments, connect with colleagues across disciplines, and learn about the exciting events, symposia, and activities planned throughout Research Month.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>This is a wonderful opportunity to build new collaborations, strengthen existing partnerships, and preview the innovative scholarship and impactful research that will be showcased in the weeks ahead. Come network, celebrate, and help us officially launch Research Month together.</p>

